025.jpg 1536w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0404-coronavirus-debt-2048x1367.jpg 2048w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0404-coronavirus-debt-2400x1602.jpg 2400w" data-src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0404-coronavirus-debt-1200x801.jpg" loading="lazy">
