<article class="row hentry post-269652 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-op-ed tag-covid-19 tag-debt tag-economic-stimulus tag-medical-debt tag-stimulus-package tag-student-debt-crisis tag-unemployment section-economy-and-labor primary_topic-economy" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/OpinionNewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/why-covid-19-could-trigger-a-major-billing-crisis/" title="Why COVID-19 Could Trigger a Surprise Billing Crisis">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="A woman holds her head and looks at bills" loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-1200x900.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/op-ed/' rel='category' class='op-ed'>Op-Ed</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/environment-and-health/' rel='section' class='environment-and-health' style='color: #0ba864;'>Environment &amp; Health</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/why-covid-19-could-trigger-a-major-billing-crisis/">Why COVID-19 Could Trigger a Surprise Billing Crisis</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Third-party companies that bill for out-of-network care stand to profit from the pandemic, at the expense of the ill.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
