<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/a-new-generation-is-rising-up-to-resist-neoliberalism-across-the-globe/">A New Generation Is Rising Up to Resist Neoliberalism Across the Globe</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">In Chile, Ecuador, Lebanon, Haiti, Iraq and beyond, international working-class solidarity is growing.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/nicholas-powers/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Nicholas Powers</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://truthout.org' itemprop='url'>Truthout</a></span></dd>
</dl>
